---
title: Honey Chipotle Double Jumbo Shrimp Bowls with Black Bean Rice and Pepper Salsa
description: Fresh and vibrant, this dinner has it all! Jumbo shrimp tossed in a smoky sauce sits on top of black beans and rice. Topped off with a roasted red pepper salsa with a hint of lime, this dish is packed with Mexican-inspired flavour.
